32/"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline">Breach of Faith: Marks &amp; Spencer GM feed undermines Plan A reputation</span></a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal">”</span></h2><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt">and</span></p><h2 style="margin:0.1pt 0pt; orphans:0; page-break-after:avoid; widows:0"><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal">GM Freeze, 8 July 2013. “</span><a href="http://www.gmfreeze.org/news-releases/233/"><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline">Sainsbury’s GM Betrayal: Dodging the ‘dif</span><span style="color:#0000ff; font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal; text-decoration:underline">ficult question’, breaking promises</span></a><span style="font-family:Arial; font-size:10pt; font-weight:normal">”</span></h2><p style="margin:0pt"><span style="font-family:'Times New Roman'; font-size:10pt">&#xa0;</span></p></body></html>